Feedback on themes:
- way too many “small creature” decks. i think you can increase the threshold. if you think about it, do you hear a lot of people saying “yeah, i’m building a deck with lots of small creatures!” — it happens, but not a ton
 - cedh — i looked at the code, the results are reasonable, but we should cut this for now until we come up with something more solid. this is the kind of thing we could “lose some cred” on if we don’t get it right
i noticed small creatures was picking up elf and goblin tribals
- energy counters deck threshold can probably be lower than 20. maybe try 15? there aren’t many decks in there.
i did show a draft of cEDH to Dan from LabManiacs to tell me if the results were sane, he said good overall, but had some specific notes
by his last survey, they run Mana Crypt 100%
im just not sure if i want to even include cedh in themes
like cedh + self mill, or one commander with two cedh builds
i think it should be its own thing
ok cool, i figured it might get a little controversy
its not that i dont like it, it’s just the thing we _have to get right_ or we might lose cred
something like self mill if we screw up a bit nobody is going to care
- self mill deck count seems low, maybe lower threshold?
- historic decks seems completely busted
historic previously was grabbing lots of artifact decks so i raised the threshold
now it looks like gods
yeah :confused:
if update_themes has finished, i can tweak by a small amount to verify that not many decks are changing type... since we were seeing a lot to changes earlier

here are my suggestions to get this wrapped up:
 - lets remove small creatures; i’m not sure if this is a viable theme overall given what i see with the results w/ weenie tribes
 - remove cedh for now; these results though are VERY promising
 - lower threshold to energy to 15
 - self mill, lets lower the threshold by 5
 - historic…i have a suggestion. i think if legendary is mentioned in the card text that’s really important. Make that +1. Also, you aren’t checking if the word “historic” is in the card text. Make that +1. Make Legendary sorceries +1 because they require historic cards to be out.
i think this is good though, like let’s make those changes to themes and next nightly i think we can keep. right now it’s a bit broken looking in some of these
we can tweak more but after these changes i’m happy with it and would announce the newness of it ^
